reviews.reviewText: By far my most favorite (and most importantly, useful) makeup bag. reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 5, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect for travel!
reviews.reviewText: The bag is very lightweight, but it is roomy enough to fit many cosmetics and skin care items for a trip. You can even add makeup brushes into the slots included in the lower portion of the bag. It even has a handle, in case you want to carry it with you separately from your other bags. The bag is very soft, made of a silicone material that feels nice to the touch. The price is definitely reasonable for this quality bag, especially compared to others similar to it that are twice the price!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 30, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Super cute and functional
reviews.reviewText: This bag is really adorable and I love the feeling of it. The texture is really smooth and soft and the top has a ribbed texture. I like how the brush compartment at the bottom has a plastic flap that closes with Velcro to cover the brush bristles. Then there’s still room in there for more. The top compartment seems like it would fit quite a bit of stuff. I am not a super huge fan of the strap that is used. It kind of seems like it’s going to be in the way of the top compartment’s zipper a lot and I will constantly have to push it down when I go from carrying it to opening it, especially with more stuff in it. The product also comes flattened from the package so it’s kind of awkward looking and not rounded out like the pictures. I’m hoping after I use it and really fill it up it will round out and lose the flatness. I also worry that the material might not hold up that long but we will see! Overall I would still recommend it
